des:
WLXT 96.3 FM "Lite 96.3" in Petoskey, MI, is an adult contemporary-formatted radio station. Enable the skill, then say "Alexa, open lite ninety six point three".

Lite 96.3 is available to stream throughout Michigan and in most of the Midwest, but not all markets. If you hear no audio, it is because Lite 96.3 is not available in that market. Our apologies for any inconvenience and thank you for listening to Lite 96.3.
